Package checker

Class Result

java.lang.Object
checker.Result
public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
Result class is a class that stores information gathered during the elaboration phase. Such information is the types and offsets of the variables. Information whether variables are shared or not, procedures local and parameter data sizes, the number of thread calls.
Author:
Karolis Butkus
